üß† PROJECT OVERVIEW
Website name

NoteSnap

What the site is about

A product landing page for a fictional service that:

turns messy notes into clean, structured summaries.

The goal of the site is not functionality, but:

strong UI/UX

scroll-triggered animations

storytelling through text + motion

portfolio-quality design

üß± SITE STRUCTURE (SECTIONS)

We agreed on a clean, limited number of sections:

Hero section

Combined Problem + Solution section

Features / Benefits section

How It Works section

Call To Action (CTA)

Footer

1Ô∏è‚É£ HERO SECTION
Purpose

