2Ô∏è‚É£ COMBINED PROBLEM + SOLUTION SECTION (CORE SECTION)

This is the main creative section of the site.

Purpose

Show problems AND solutions together

Tell a story with scroll

Sync text (left) with visual animation (right)

Layout

Left 50%: text

Right 50%: animated visuals (notes + robot)

Left Side (Text)

The text appears step by step as you scroll.

Each problem is followed by its solution.

Example structure:

Problem 1:

‚ÄúToo many scribbles. Notes get lost.‚Äù

Solution 1:

‚ÄúNoteSnap organizes everything instantly.‚Äù

Problem 2:

‚ÄúImportant details buried in chaos.‚Äù

Solution 2:

‚ÄúFind what matters at a glance.‚Äù

Problem 3:

‚ÄúSharing notes is slow and messy.‚Äù

Solution 3:

‚ÄúOne click to share clean notes.‚Äù

Text animations

Each line:

fades in

slides slightly from bottom or side

Problems and solutions are separate scroll moments

Right Side (Visual Representation)

This side reacts to the text.

Visual concept

Notes are DOM or SVG elements

At first:

scattered

rotated

messy

When solution text appears:

notes align

stack

snap into order

Robot role (illusion-based interaction)

Robot does NOT physically grab notes

Robot:

looks at notes

tilts head

moves arm slightly

Notes animate in sync ‚Üí illusion of interaction

