ü§ñ CHARACTER (ROBOT)
What it is

SVG-based robot character

Not a photo

Not 3D

Built from simple shapes

Style

Hand-drawn look (like CAIDE‚Äôs dog)

Outline only

Black or dark gray stroke

Minimal shading

Friendly, curious personality

Structure (important)

The SVG is grouped into parts:

head

eyes

body

left arm

right arm

left leg

right leg

This allows animation.

Animations used

Floating

Head tilt

Arm rotation

Simple walking illusion (leg swing + body bob)

Eye blink / look direction

üé® COLOR PALETTE

We didn‚Äôt lock one, but recommended:

Background: white or #FDFDFD

Text:  #151515

Accent color: ONE bright color
Action color: #3B82F6
and also: Soft Gray #F5F5F5

